name: tiny world: varian
description: the pandemic closed the commercial world; however, it opened the natural one.   each moment of j.w’s 25th year presented opportunity for us to explore the uncontained and immortal beauty of the wilderness. both familiar and foreign fields beheld pictures which were never seen before, and which shall never be seen again.   through our journeys across the great american west, we learned it matters not where you go but instead who is beside you.
